  <summary>GCompris teachers companion</summary>
  <description>
    <p>GCompris-teachers is a companion application for teachers to enhance their use of GCompris in their classroom.</p>
    <p>It allows teachers to create customized datasets and receive pupils
    results for some activities.</p>
  </description>
